{"tid":2324062,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【沈旭暉】西藏1959 Vs 香港2019：「一國兩制」終結的一個劇本，兩個故事","createTime":"2020-12-13T16:01:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T13:55:02.000Z","uid":278587,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"830ca492bd74934b201a7021ea9bd363116c94a9","tid":2324062,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T16:01:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fk6ZbZvY_uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dfk6ZbZvY_uk&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725IWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=b2067657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fk6ZbZvY_uk</a><br />\n<br />\n【#堅離地球YouTube】香港「二次回歸」，劇情似曾相識，1959年的西藏，幾乎一模一樣的進行過一次。可以想像，在未來的「政治正確版」國民教育教科書，官方口中的「1959年西藏暴亂」和「2019年香港黑暴」，都是分別實質上終結兩地「一國兩制」的導火線。至於民間論述，自然只能靠民間流傳。從中，也可見中央政府對待邊地的手法，始終如一。我們可簡單比較如下。"},{"pid":"30ea64f8828f30f87651c53cba04031251d898d4","tid":2324062,"uid":89267,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T16:05:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba8231989285243aa254e4ba37e965ca0dbbf7e5","tid":2324062,"uid":92188,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T16:08:52.000Z","msg":"大家早啲走，除非你想好似啲藏民咁樣自焚，係自焚都冇用啦"},{"pid":"761d36ea5c3f9bd0eaeb881336116dbdee490064","tid":2324062,"uid":291750,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T16:29:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65756a84187998715945a2f0670e17a2ca4aaaa8","tid":2324062,"uid":161185,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T23:30:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53693f0ae6829c845a966cc1e3dd0611